description: Demolition of the existing buildings and redevelopment of the site, involving the erection of a building of part-five/part-six storeys (including lower ground floor level) fronting Clapham Road stepping down to four storeys (including lower ground floor level) fronting Jeffreys Road, and 18 three and four-storey houses within the site to provide a mixed use scheme incorporating office (B1 Use Class), retail (A1 Use Class), and cafe (A3 Use Class) uses to provide 2,785sqm of commercial space, together with 69 residential units (including 28 affordable units) and associated access, servicing, refuse storage, car and cycle parking, and landscaped amenity areas. (This application is a departure from policy S3 of the Core Strategy 2011).
